{"tid":2074282,"cid":5,"subCid":10,"title":"譚耀宗︰日後公務員就任須宣誓擁護基本法","createTime":"2020-06-22T03:47:16.000Z","updateTime":"2020-06-22T05:34:29.000Z","uid":20933,"like":1,"dislike":9,"uniUserReply":9,"replies":[{"pid":"16ee81e534738b4006169499e3de5c944e408cd7","tid":2074282,"uid":20933,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-06-22T03:47:16.000Z","msg":"【Now新聞台】港區國安法草案草案說明指，日後參選或就任公職時，應依法簽署文件確認或宣誓擁護基本法。人大常委譚耀宗認為包括公務員，至於現職公務員是否需要宣誓，他就指不清楚。<br />\n<br />\n人大常委譚耀宗：「這個沒有說得很清楚，出任，即剛上任，還是現任，因為字眼出任，總之作為公務員大家都責任，公務員不只特區，亦是中央的，是中華人民共和國下的特區。」"},{"pid":"f57936ee105b45650bf6a7070533647e501b6fc8","tid":2074282,"uid":20933,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-06-22T03:47:24.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://news.now.com/mobile/editorsChoice/player?newsId=395313\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fnews.now.com%2Fmobile%2FeditorsChoice%2Fplayer%3FnewsId%3D395313&d=oSWSjOI%2Bg%2Fd3CLQu9eb0F8TiFwqRwBg1VWT7Je45URE%3D&h=e200e850\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fnews.now.com%2Fmobile%2FeditorsChoice%2Fplayer%3FnewsId%3D395313&h=78f0c796\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://news.now.com/mobile/editorsChoice/player?newsId=395313</a>"},{"pid":"a3f7517a2c38a0eb761be06cab6f79d6b5e422b1","tid":2074282,"uid":155095,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-06-22T03:51:06.000Z","msg":"公務員不只特區，亦是中央的 <img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/touch.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n香港公務員可以加入中國共產黨 <img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/wet.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"e06adcc4cf8bc23bdd23ea18d0cfcd51a3864f05","tid":2074282,"uid":133743,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-06-22T03:54:59.000Z","msg":"支持公務員宣誓效忠習大大<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"11cfeb9fd6dce96b6bb2fb2d32804db39fc3c56a","tid":2074282,"uid":54800,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-06-22T03:55:20.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"http://vignette3.wikia.noc